<!doctype html>

<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">

  <title>Mobamura Character-Player list tool</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/image/favicon.ico">
  <link href="https://unpkg.com/tabulator-tables/dist/css/tabulator.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/tabulator-tables/dist/js/tabulator.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <h2></h2>
    <h2>ボタン</h2>
    <p>連携先ツールに負担がかかるため、連打は禁止とします</p>
    <div>
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" rel="nofollow" onClick="table.replaceData('/result/cinderella_cute.json')">シンデレラガールズ（Cu属性）</a>
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" rel="nofollow" onClick="table.replaceData('/result/cinderella_cool.json')">シンデレラガールズ（Co属性）</a>
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" rel="nofollow" onClick="table.replaceData('/result/cinderella_passion.json')">シンデレラガールズ（Pa属性）</a>
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" rel="nofollow" onClick="table.replaceData('/result/cinderella_another.json')">シンデレラガールズ（その他）</a>
    </div>
    <div>
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" rel="nofollow" onClick="table.replaceData('/result/sidem.json')">ディアリースターズ、および、SideM</a>
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" rel="nofollow" onClick="table.replaceData('/result/shinycolors.json')">シャイニーカラーズ</a>
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" rel="nofollow" onClick="table.replaceData('/result/million.json')">ミリオンライブ、その他</a>
    </div>
    <h2>結果</h2>
    <div id="result_table"></div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
    var tabledata = [];
    var table = new Tabulator("#result_table",{
        data:tabledata,
        columns:[
            {title:"キャラクター名（CN）", field:"cn"},
            {title:"プレイヤー名（HN or TRIP）", field:"player"},
            {title:"村参加回数", field:"count"},
            {title:"キャラクター使用回数順位", field:"rank"},
        ]
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>